                    <h3
                        class="font-serif text-2xl mb-3 text-forest group-hover:text-coral transition-colors"
                    >
                        Project Name
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-forest/70 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                        Brief description of the project and the technologies
                        used. Focusing on backend or frontend specifics.
                    </p>
